Dutch — assets/examples/dutch_M40K1FS28A.{wav,phn}
    IFA Spoken Language Corpus (R.J.J.H. van Son et al., Institute of Phonetic
    Sciences, University of Amsterdam). Released under the GNU GPL v2 or later
